---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | MyBlog">
  <main class="about-container">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1>About <span class="text-gradient">MyBlog</span></h1>
      <p>Learn more about who we are and what we do.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="/images/author.jpg" alt="Blog Author" />
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>Hello, I'm Alex</h2>
        <p>I'm a web developer and technical writer with over 8 years of experience in the industry. I created this blog to share my knowledge, experiences, and insights about web development and design.</p>
        
        <p>My journey in web development began when I was in college, tinkering with HTML and CSS to create simple websites. Since then, I've worked with various technologies and frameworks, from vanilla JavaScript to React, Vue, and now Astro.</p>
        
        <h3>What I Write About</h3>
        <p>On this blog, you'll find articles about:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Web development best practices</li>
          <li>Frontend frameworks and libraries</li>
          <li>Performance optimization</li>
          <li>User experience design</li>
          <li>Career advice for developers</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>My Mission</h3>
        <p>My goal is to make web development more accessible and enjoyable for everyone. Whether you're a beginner just starting out or an experienced developer looking to stay updated with the latest trends, I hope you'll find valuable content here.</p>
        
        <div class="skills">
          <h3>Skills & Expertise</h3>
          <div class="skill-tags">
            <span class="skill-tag">HTML/CSS</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">JavaScript</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">TypeScript</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">React</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Vue</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Node.js</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Astro</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">UI/UX Design</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="contact-cta">
      <h2>Want to get in touch?</h2>
      <p>Feel free to reach out if you have questions, suggestions, or just want to say hello!</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="contact-button">Contact Me</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .text-gradient {
    background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-size: 400%;
    background-position: 0%;
  }
  
  .about-header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #ddd;
  }
  
  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }
  
  .about-text h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
  }
  
  .about-text h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }
  
  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height:1.7;
  }
  
  .about-text ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .about-text li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .skills {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .skill-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }
  
  .skill-tag {
    background-color: rgba(var(--accent), 0.1);
    color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  
  .contact-cta {
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #23262d;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .contact-cta h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .contact-cta p {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  
  .contact-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: rgb(var(--accent));
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .contact-button:hover {
    background-color: rgb(var(--accent-dark));
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .about-image {
      max-width: 300px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
